	(35916,'Sustainability Problems',147,4270,'In this course, students will map the matrix of problems that make sustainability difficult ? problems with the U.S. political, legal, and educational system, with media, culture, and individual behavior. Students will also identify sustainability pathways in transportation, urban design, education, alternative energy, etc. Throughout, students will analyze and try to produce effective environmental communication.',NULL,NULL,'spring',2015),
