	(35955,'Foundations of Human-Computer Interaction Usa',145,6420,'This course will consider methods for gathering users? requirements for product functions and information, ways to test products and information for usability and suitability, and procedures for incorporating the results learned through testing. Students will design and conduct usability tests on products, documents, and interfaces of interest.',NULL,NULL,'spring',2015),
