	(36186,'INTRO TO PROB GRAPHICAL METHOD',142,6810,'',NULL,NULL,'spring',2015),
	(36187,'Statistical Mechanics',133,6590,'Review of thermodynamics, probability, and statistics. Statistical basis of thermodynamics, various ensembles, quantum statistics. Ideal Fermi and Bose gases and applications to solids and the black-body radiation. Interacting systems, phase transitions, and critical phenomena. Phase transition in the Van der Waals gas and in the Ising ferromagnet. Mean-field approximation and Landau theory of continuous phase transitions. Random walk, diffusion, Brownian motion, and Langevin equation. Stochastic processes.',NULL,NULL,'spring',2015),
